data.description: **Charming 3 Bed, 2 Bath Home with Partial Finished Basement**  Discover potential in this North College Hill gem, conveniently located near highways for easy commuting. Boasting hardwood floors and newer kitchen/bath flooring, this residence offers a solid foundation for customization. TLC and cosmetic touches needed. Previous water intrusion addressed; fascia repaired. Important Notice: Back deck requires repair, and stairs to deck are currently unattached. Renovation opportunity for the savvy buyer. All appliances included, presenting an enticing opportunity for owner-occupants or savvy fix-and-flip investors. Act now!. Don't miss out!
